title: Affordable and very large 1 bedroom- private, cute, amazing
posting_body: ['Hey there!', 'I am moving out of the state and looking for someone to fill my spot and begin a new lease (no lease takeover).', "I've lived here a couple months and absolutely love it but need to move for work.", 'plus, its really affordable for how big it is.', 'Judah and 23rd Ave- not too deep in the sunset, lots of great food near by, easy parking (no permit, just some street cleaning never been an issue), right by park, quiet neighborhood and 7 bus and N line right outside your door (but the unit is near the back', "so you hear absolutely nothing), the COOLEST BATHROOM IN SF- overall my favorite place I've lived in SF and hope to fill with someone kind, likeminded, cool, clean, and responsible!", 'Landlord is very nice and communicative, and there is also a shared backyard that gets so much sun!', 'admittedly its a really small kitchen.', 'I have an airfrier and it works fine, and the landlord can provide a strong toaster oven', 'I am also open to selling some furniture if you want to move in and keep some things I have.', 'Pics of empty unit plus some with my furniture in it - let me know if you need any furniture.', 'timeline is slightly flexible but aiming for October 1 move in.', 'can be earlier if needed.', 'there is also a security deposit equivalent to 1 month rent', 'note from the landlord for application:', 'Maximum 2 people,rent $1850/month', 'Have the following prepared to present to the Manager of Building:', '1.', 'Cover letter describing your situation', '2.', 'With photocopies of the following:', "Driver's License or Passport", 'Credit Report with FICO score from: <URL>', '<URL>', '<URL>', '<URL>', '3.', 'Most recent pay stub or job offer letter with Start Date and Salary and a clear idea of total annual household income', '4.', 'Bank statement or financial statement reflecting savings/financial aid/ student loan/guarantor financial information if any(for student)', '5.', "Previous Landlord's name, phone #, and address (best time to call)", '6.', "Employer's name, phone #, and address.", "Also your supervisor's name and phone #."]
